# Description
# -----------
#
#  Completion script for _vim_files
#
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Authors
# -------
#
#  * Hector Lecuanda (https://github.com/hlecuanda)
#
#  Based on code for _jq completion by:
#  * Hideaki Miyake (https://github.com/mollifier)
#  * George Kontridze (https://github.com/gkze)
#
